window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Monsters don't hide in dark alleys.</b></p> <p>They lurk in plain sight, clawing into your soul with cordial smiles. They wear Armani, they drive Cadillacs, they attend fundraising balls... And they rule the city with a merciless fist.</p> <p>The Familia is a mystery to most, and sitting on its throne is Kage Malvagio. Vile. Sadistic. Painstakingly beautiful.</p> <p>Some say: Ask for forgiveness, never permission. Kage asks for neitherâ€”especially when he gets his hands on me.</p> <p>I should hate him. I should run at the first chance I get. But how could the devil be so bad when he looks at me like that?</p> <p>From <i>USA Today</i> bestselling author Kelsey Clayton comes a dark mafia romance filled with pain, betrayal, devastation, and revenge. <i>Suffer in Silence</i> is book one of the Malvagio Mafia Duet and ends on a cliffhanger. This dark romance deals with topics that are not for the faint of heart.</p>"; 
